Q: Cessna 150属于哪种机型类型（如远程、小飞机）？
SQL: SELECT aircraft_type_match.aircraft_type FROM aircraft_type_match INNER JOIN dc_aircraft_model ON aircraft_type_match.`code` = dc_aircraft_model.aircraft_type WHERE name = "Cessna 150" LIMIT 1;
